   inherit kde-v4
   require kde-runtime
  category educational
 attribute makej
    source   stable $KDE_URL   stable/$VERSION/src/$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.xz
    source unstable $KDE_URL unstable/$VERSION/src/$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.xz
      desc 'an educational programming environment
kturtle aims to make learning how to program as easy as possible.
To achieve this kturtle makes all programming tools
available from the user interface.
The programming language used is turtlescript
which allows its commands to be translated.'
